PHP-to-multi-messengers application

'core' is framework folder, 'messengers' is application folder

Installation:
1. open messenger/config/config.php in editor and change your database settings
2. run console commands:
messenger/app/ztool db:init
messenger/app/ztool db:migrate


How to use:
To run daemon type messengers/app/daemon
To run console type messenger/app/run and follow on-screen instructions